---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout pageTitle="Presentations">
    <div class="page-container">
        <h1>Presentations</h1>

        <p class="intro-text">
            I present regularly at interspecies mechanics conferences, mythical conservation forums, and
            biomechanics symposia. I have yet to give a talk where at least one audience member did not
            initially assume the subject matter was not serious. By the end, none of them make that
            mistake twice.
        </p>

        <section>
            <h2>Keynote Addresses</h2>
            <ul class="custom-list">
                <li>
                    <a class="list-item-title" href={`${base}presentations/hoot-purr-overlap-zone.html`}>
                        The Hoot-Purr Overlap Zone: Acoustic Convergence Across Biological Kingdoms
                    </a>
                    <span class="list-item-description">
                        Plenary Keynote — International Symposium on Interspecies Physics, Geneva, 2026
                        <span class="extra-links">
                            Presenting the full unified field theory of low-frequency vibration; accompanied by live spectrograms from field recordings of synchronised owl-cat vocalisation events
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a class="list-item-title" href={`${base}presentations/soft-matter-hard-science.html`}>
                        Soft Matter, Hard Science: Redefining Biomechanical Parameters for Fluffy Systems
                    </a>
                    <span class="list-item-description">
                        Opening Keynote — Annual Meeting of the Society for Theoretical Zoology, Edinburgh, 2024
                        <span class="extra-links">
                            Overview of the Kinematics of Soft Systems framework and its application across avian, feline, and mythical taxa
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Conference Presentations</h2>
            <ul class="custom-list">
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Mapping the Bioluminescent Corridors: Three Years of Unicorn Migration Data
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">Monoceros Initiative Symposium, Reykjavík, 2025</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        η<sub>loaf</sub> = 0.94: Why the Loaf Position Is an Evolutionary Optimum
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">Advanced Biomechanics of Cuteness Conference, Amsterdam, 2024</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Bio-Fluidic Solids: Empirical Evidence for the Liquid Cat Hypothesis
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">Journal of Non-Newtonian Biomechanics Annual Conference, Zurich, 2022</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Wing-Loading Limits for Large Mythical Ungulates: A Finite-Element Approach
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">Proceedings of the Institute of Mythical Aerodynamics, Virtual, 2021</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Stardust Lattices: Novel Photonic Microstructures in High-Altitude Mythical Fauna
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">Theoretical Zoology Review Colloquium, Vienna, 2023</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Seminars &amp; Colloquia</h2>
            <ul class="custom-list">
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Silent Flight, Silent Stalk: A Comparative Predator Kinematics Seminar
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">
                        Laboratory for Avian &amp; Feline Dynamics, Institute of Mythical Studies, 2025
                        <span class="extra-links">
                            Internal seminar introducing the S<sub>f</sub>/S<sub>s</sub> comparative framework to new lab members and visiting fellows
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Fluff-Density Tomography: Protocol and Calibration Workshop
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">
                        Department of Theoretical Zoology, University of Owlford, 2019
                        <span class="extra-links">
                            Hands-on workshop introducing the FDT protocol; now adopted as the departmental standard for soft-tissue biomechanical scanning
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="list-item-title">
                        Field Observation Without Disturbance: 500 Hours Among Barn Owls and Barn Cats
                    </span>
                    <span class="list-item-description">
                        Mythical Conservation Society Annual Lecture, London, 2022
                        <span class="extra-links">
                            Public lecture presented upon receipt of the Apex Observer Award; covered methodology, findings, and ethical field protocols
                        </span>
                    </span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>
</Layout>
